                    "text": "<p>We do farmer's markets and pop-up events throughout the year — it's our favorite way to connect with customers and let people smell the collection before they buy. Follow us on <a href=\"https://instagram.com/emberwoodandhearth\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://instagram.com/emberwoodandhearth\">Instagram</a> or check back here for our current schedule. We don't offer local pickup outside of those events.</p>",
